data.description:
Welcome to 1622 W Owens Way, Anthem, AZ 85086!
This remarkable 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in the Anthem Country Club offers an exceptional living experience.
Situated adjacent to a tranquil wash and green space, it provides an unparalleled level of privacy. The open great room design creates a spacious and inviting atmosphere, with the master suite thoughtfully separated from the other bedrooms.
Other highlights include a new Fridge, Washer,Dryer and microwave, a cozy firepit for outdoor gatherings, a soft water system, and an abundance of windows that fill the home with natural light. The landscaping is designed for easy maintenance, featuring established vegetation.
Anthem Country Club's numerous amenities are just a stone's throw away, 
Click on MORE offering pools, clubhouses, two restaurants, an 18-hole golf course, pro shops, spas, dry saunas, steam rooms, tennis courts, a fitness club, massage services, and much more!
This is your chance to experience the epitome of resort-style living. Contact us today to arrange a private viewing.
